last_episode_to_air.name: Mischevious Sabotage
last_episode_to_air.overview: Determined to get into the film academy, Max , an aspiring filmmaker brings together a group of friends to help him with his college entry piece. However a more sinister plan is already underway.

name: Wicked Enigma
overview: Something Wicked this way comes! This LGBTQ suspense thriller has the drama of Pretty Little Liars with the horror elements of Scream. Our sassy and troubled heroes are far from heroic as they try to keep the murder a secret. Max must survive betrayal, love, loss and grief while being a pawn of an even more WICKED game. But when everyone has a motive, who do you suspect?
